INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('10101', '加拿大Agriculex ESC-1电动种子数粒仪', '101', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2.5;font-size:24px;color:#9BCF08;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">产品特点</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1．数粒速度快。在合理、准确的连续模式下，对大多数种子，每秒数粒超过</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">100</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">粒。当批次计数时，速度要降低到小批量精度情况下；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">2．在低的数粒速度下，仪器是非常准确的；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">3．当更换种子时，可快速、简单的清除；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">4．适合种子的大小非常广泛，从直径</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1mm</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">到超过</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">10mm</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">，包括油菜籽、小谷物、玉米和大豆；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">5．静音、低粉尘、低功率消耗。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#9BCF08;font-size:18px;\">操作模式</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"width:570px;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"48\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">序号</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"192\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">操作模式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"360\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">说   明</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"48\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:\" line-height:2;color:#666666;\"=\"\">1</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"192\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">连续模式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"360\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  用于计算样品种子的总数。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"48\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:\" line-height:2;color:#666666;\"=\"\">2</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"192\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">自动进料控制批处理模式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"360\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  这个模式用来计数具有特定大小的批量种子。</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  每一个批次后，机器都要停下，操作简单。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"48\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:\" line-height:2;color:#666666;\"=\"\">3</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"192\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">连续进料批处理模式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"360\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  这是批量计数的另一个模式。操作远比自动</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  进料控制要快，但是操作者要调整到一个他</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  们可以跟上的速度，因为机器要在一批种子</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  计数完成后才能进行下一批。已数完的种子</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  保存在机器的内部，直到操作者用一个容器</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  把种子放出。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"48\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:\" line-height:2;color:#666666;\"=\"\">4</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"192\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">分割样品到一定数目模式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"360\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  用于把样品数一个特定的量。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">  此模式需要一些可选功能。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2.5;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"></span><span></span> \r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/a772b891-1948-4753-8fba-cd2fec657f96.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('10102', '加拿大Agriculex ESC-2可编程电子数粒仪', '101', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">产品介绍</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">ESC-2型与</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">ESC-1</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">型区别是增加了可以连接计算机进行编程数粒的功能和通过随机的条形码自动识别的功能。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">产品特点</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1．拥有</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">16</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">个计数通道。每个通道都配有一个红外线传感器。控制箱有一个</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">RS - 232</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">端口。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">2．可以预先设置种子的数量，在</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">连续</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">模式，也可以用来找出种子在预加权或容积测量部分的总数。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">3．能够读取条形码，存储和检索的计数信息，以及在计算机上远程操作</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">ESC-\r\n2</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">数粒仪。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">4．能够以极高的速度进行数粒，并且不会降低数粒精度。速度较慢时，数粒极为准确。计数速度可调。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">5．良好的用户界面，操作方便快速。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">6．设备易于清理。在更换种子的时候，能够提供剩余种子的数量。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">7．当一个批次数粒接近结束时，设备会自动降低数粒速度，并及时切断，使数粒更为精确。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">8．处理的种子直径大小从约</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1mm</span><span> </span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">到</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">10mm</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">的范围，包括油菜、小杂粮、玉米、大豆、</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">     小麦等。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">9．低噪音、低尘、低功耗。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">使用范围</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">目前已广泛应用于</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">先锋、先正大、孟山都</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">等种业集团。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/783b3bc1-0829-4a9d-af52-9682b4ea3ddb.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('10103', '日本AIDEX全自动谷物数粒仪', '101', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#9BCF08;font-size:18px;line-height:2;\">产品介绍</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">AIDEX</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">全自动谷物数粒仪</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">可用于各类种子的计数，如花、草、蔬菜、玉米、稻谷、大豆、小麦等种子的计数，是种子、颗粒计数的精密仪器设备，可用于育种实验室，也可作为成套生产设备，减少人工强度。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">该设备也可用于其它颗粒计数领域或电子器件的计数。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">可计量进料盘颗粒的总数，也可用于给定数量的分包装。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;line-height:2;\">说明</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">全自动谷物数粒仪</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">测定种类：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">小麦、水稻、玉米、大豆、杂粮等各类作物种子，也可计数电子零件。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/upload/image/image/20190926/20190926090543_167.gif\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">              采用长型光幕感测器，每一个种子落下时，会产生一个波纹。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">                                 <img src=\"/upload/image/image/20190926/20190926090648_35.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"177\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">           种子投入圆形转盘后，种子会因振动而自动整列，成螺旋状上升。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#9BCF08;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;\">可</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;\">调整感度</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#666666;\">                      <img src=\"/upload/image/image/20190926/20190926091010_491.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"246\" height=\"196\" title=\"\" /> <b><b><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span></b></b><br />\r\n</span></b> \r\n	<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"528\" style=\"text-align:center;width:396pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td width=\"168\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">可调灵敏度对象</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"204\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">平均速度（种子</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">分钟）</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"156\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">传感器灵敏度</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td width=\"168\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.55pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">莴苣种子</span><span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"204\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">300</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"156\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">非常高</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\"> (SS)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td width=\"168\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.55pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">甘蓝种子、糙米</span><span></span></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"204\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">1000</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"156\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">高</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">(S)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td width=\"168\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.55pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">水稻种子、小麦</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"204\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">700</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"156\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">中等</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">(M)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td width=\"168\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.55pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">大豆、玉米</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"204\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">300</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"156\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n					<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">低(L)</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b></b> \r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/74407150-9470-4a94-9230-cd74e2684a25.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('10301', '种研BY-P2000型种子包衣机', '103', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;line-height:2;\">产品介绍</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:19.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;line-height:3;font-size:16px;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent:27pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2.5;\">种研</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2.5;\">BY-P2000</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2.5;\">型种子包衣机适合于包衣量不大，但使用次数频繁的用户。整机结构紧凑，体积小，重量轻，操作简单。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent:27pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2.5;\">该机型物料和药液搅拌均匀，连续喂入，供药量调整简单、直观，药种配比准确。针对高寒地区，可提供专用加温药液桶。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:19.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;line-height:3;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:19.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;line-height:3;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:19.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#666666;line-height:3;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/ba20c179-8f19-4052-9adb-0271343ca819.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('10302', '种研BY-L3小型种子包衣机', '103', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">产品介绍</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"> <span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">本机型适用于对小批量、多批次种子进行包衣处理，特别是对少量小粒种子，通过丸粒化处理，增大种子体积，便于机械化播种</span>。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">性能特点</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1．药种配比精确，零破碎，易清洗，自动化程度高，省时省力。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">2．种子包衣机利用混合钵底部转盘的高速旋转，带动钵中物料上下滚动和颗粒之间的相互运动；当钵中物料加入一定量预先计量的种衣剂时，就会使用种衣剂均匀包敷在物料的表面上，形成一定厚度的胶膜并牢固敷在物料的表面。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">3．根据试验种子的不同，可以将药种比设定为</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">40-200</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">，通过设定种子在钵内的混合时间和调整混合钵底部转盘的运行速度等方式，使种子达到理想的包衣效果。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">4．控制面板上有机器启动按钮、转盘转速旋钮和转盘时间设定旋钮。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.55pt;text-indent:-20.5pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/4c812489-2a0a-431a-99b1-ad4076ab4dfc.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('20101', '力垦2BZL-6(A)型自走式数控小区条播播种机', '201', '<p style=\"margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">产品简介</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.3pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">力垦2BZL-6(A)型自走式数控小区条播播种机设计理念先进，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">年通过河南省农机局组织的技术鉴定</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">鉴定证书号</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">2014YJ039)</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">， 申报国家专利</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;line-height:2;\">项，整机制造工艺精湛，整体技术性能已领先于国外进口同类机型性能。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.3pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">性能特点</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">1．专为作物育种试验和产品比对试验设计生产，播种效果及精准度完全符合小区育种试验要求；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">2．准确实现定量播种，即在规定播行内，按规定的行距、播深精确播完某一品系的定量种子；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">3．精准的行长控制功能，对播种行长可进行厘米级的无级调控，确保精准度；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">4．出色的自净功能，确保实现无混杂播种。自净功能使不同品系的种子不会残留在种子箱和排种器内，避免造成种子混杂；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">5．播量、播深均匀一致，有利于提高出苗质量，提高试验准确性；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">6．划印宽度和行距设置简单方便；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">7．使用不同的分种系统可以在小区内进行选择性多行播种；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">8．具有出色的通用性，通过换装不同的分配系统和模块，可以实现播种不同形状的种子；</span><b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">9．具有多种开沟系统，适用在不同的土壤条件下进行播种；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">10．操作简便，播种过程中驾驶人员和操作人员均可以清楚了解播种情况，对播种进程进行实时监控。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">11．安装单粒播种转换框架即可做为单粒播种机使用。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">12．可以根据客户的需求，量身订制个性化解决方案，定制客户需要的机型。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/ae19a7a0-4699-4271-9277-52a3e64fe6f3.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('20102', '力垦2BZL-6(B)型自走式数控小区条播播种机', '201', '<p style=\"margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#9BCF08;font-size:18px;\">产品简介</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.3pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">力垦2BZL-6</span><span class=\"headline2\" style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">(B)</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">型自走式数控小区条播播种机设计理念先进，</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">2014</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">年通过河南省农机局组织的技术鉴定</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">(</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">鉴定证书号</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">2014YJ039)</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">， 申报国家专利</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">项，整机制造工艺精湛，整体技术性能已领先于国外进口同类机型性能。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.3pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;\">性能特点</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">1．专为作物育种试验和产品比对试验设计生产，播种效果及精准度完全符合小区育种试验要求；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">2．准确实现定量播种，即在规定播行内，按规定的行距、播深精确播完某一品系的定量种子；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">3．精准的行长控制功能，对播种行长可进行厘米级的无级调控，确保精准度；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">4．出色的自净功能，确保实现无混杂播种。自净功能使不同品系的种子不会残留在种子箱和排种器内，避免造成种子混杂；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">5．播量、播深均匀一致，有利于提高出苗质量，提高试验准确性；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">6．划印宽度和行距设置简单方便；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">7．使用不同的分种系统可以在小区内进行选择性多行播种；</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">8．具有出色的通用性，通过换装不同的分配系统和模块，可以实现播种不同形状的种子；</span><b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">9．具有多种开沟系统，适用在不同的土壤条件下进行播种；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">10．操作简便，播种过程中驾驶人员和操作人员均可以清楚了解播种情况，对播种进程进行实时监控。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">11．安装单粒播种转换框架即可做为单粒播种机使用。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;color:#666666;\">12．可以根据客户的需求，量身订制个性化解决方案，定制客户需要的机型。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/634e1052-545c-45d1-bcab-3ebefd701ca6.jpg');
INSERT INTO `cpzx` VALUES ('20201', '力垦2BZL-1250型自走式数控单粒播种机', '202', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#99BB00;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;color:#99BB00;\">产品介绍</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">        2BZL-1250</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">型自走式数控单粒播种机是力垦公司于</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">年研发生产出的最新型单粒播种机，整机具有独立自主知识产权。该产品采用最新设计理念，使用电传数控技术，完全摒弃了地轮、皮带、塔型齿轮等传统机械部件，采用智能化、数字化控制，可在触摸屏上对株距实现无级设定和精准控制，完全避免漏播和品系混杂。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;line-height:2;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">         2BZL-1250</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">型自走式数控单粒播种机由智能化数控系统、自动供种系统、伺服播种控制系统、智能调节系统、余种回收系统、单粒株距控制系统、液压控制系统和两档四车速可调动力系统组成。产品配置灵活，可根据用户的不同需求，通过更换种子托架、径向盘、窝眼盘实现单粒、双粒、单双粒播种。整机操作简便，安全可靠。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">        2BZL-1250</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">型自走式数控单粒播种机的设计理念和技术性能目前居于世界领先水平。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:2;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#B8D100;line-height:2;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#9BCF08;line-height:2;\">性能特点</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">1．专为小区育种试验设计生产，播种效果及精准度完全符合小区育种试验要求；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">2．准确实现定量播种，即在规定播行内，按规定的株距、播量、播深精确播完某一品系的定量种子；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">3．出色的自净功能，确保实现无混杂播种。自净功能使不同品系的种子不会残留在播种器</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">     和</span><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:16px;\">分种器内，避免造成种子混杂；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">4．株距、播量、播深均匀一致，有利于提高出苗质量，提高试验准确性；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">5．划印宽度、行距设置简单方便；</span><img src=\"/upload/image/image/20190918/20190918115700_869.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">6．使用不同的分种系统可以进行多行、多品种、单粒、双粒、单双粒播种；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">7．具有出色的通用性，通过换装不同的分配系统和模块，可以实现播种不同形状的种子；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">8．具有多种开沟系统，适用在不同的土壤条件下进行播种；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">9．具有多种进料方式，使机器具有更广泛的使用范围；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">10．操作简便，播种过程中驾驶人员和操作人员均可以清楚了解播种情况，对播种进程进</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">       行实时监控。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">11．安装条播播种转换框架即可做为条播播种机使用。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\">12．可以根据客户的需求，量身订制个性化解决方案，定制客户需要的机型。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;color:#666666;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 'upload/cpzx/daccfe63-adcc-4160-bc38-26488d72f63f.jpg');
