		<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">行进速度</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">具有两挡四车速可调动力系统，无级变速，速度范围：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">0</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">13km/h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">行进方式</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">自走式，电驱动。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">播种行数</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">8</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">行可选；特殊行数可定制；离心式分种器。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">播种长度</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">200</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">5000cm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">无级设定，采用智能化数控操作系统，可在</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">7</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">寸彩色触摸屏上实现</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">200</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">5000cm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">无级调控小区长度。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">排种装置</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">直径</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">406mm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">蜂窝式排种器</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">开</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">沟</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">器</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">钝角锚式、锐角锚式或双圆盘式液压升降开沟器，开沟器压力</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">0</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">16Kpa</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">；</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">0</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">～</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">8cm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">无级调节播种深度。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">转</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">向</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">器</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">液压转向装置，液压制动装置，易于操作。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">行</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">间</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">距</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">≥</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">6cm</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"102\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">其</span><span style=\"font-family:\" color:#000000;\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">他</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"466\" style=\"border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">播种机轮距大于</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">150cm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" color:#000000;\"=\"\">，配有一个驾驶座椅，一个操作座椅，座椅均配有可手动调节的安全带。</span><span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '20102');

